My resume...

1. I am Pit Fiend of HEL (Hell's Elite Legions), guildmaster (1 out of 4). www.HEL-guild.com , we are a gaming guild strictly in 1st person shooter, simulation, and strategy games games.

2. I was ranked #1 deathmatch player in Battlezone and founded HEL in 1997.

3. HEL currently plays in:
----Battlezone, formerly, undefeated #1 ranking, we OwNeD... most of our players have moved on
----Battlezone2, currently ranked #1 in strategy play, undefeated, developers of the "HEL rush", active
----Soldier of Fortune, currently ranked #1 in team deathmatch, undefeated, very active
